<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>10: I skip-counted by 2 five times: 2, 4, 6, 8, 10. </li>
      <li>12: It is one more 2 than the first problem, <m>10 + 2 = 10</m>.</li>
      <li>30: I counted by 5.</li>
      <li>35: It is one more 5 than the problem before this. </li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


